I would invite you to find one minute every day to carve one minute out every day where you're quiet.

40:39.266 --> 40:47.198
You turn off the notifications on your phone, you're not listening to music or a podcast, and you're not overwhelmed by the stuff of life.

40:47.499 --> 40:48.460
One single minute.

